.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Movie-Genre: crime, spy, thriller, satire, romance
Flower: lily, aconite, azalea, iris, orchid
Cigar: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
City: berlin, london, boston, paris, miami
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Flower:lily == Movie-Genre:crime
2. Flower:aconite == Pet:dog
3. City:berlin == Movie-Genre:spy
4. Flower:azalea == City:london
5. Movie-Genre:spy is to the right of Movie-Genre:thriller
6. Cigar:old-gold == Pet:snails
7. Cigar:kools == Movie-Genre:satire
8. City:boston is in the middle
9. Flower:iris is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == City:paris
13. Flower:orchid == Cigar:parliaments
14. Flower:iris is to the left or right of Movie-Genre:romance

